title: Charm. 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom upstairs Extra Belcony Cute Baby Bed!
posting_body: ['This is a beautiful, sunny, time honored three level townhouse duplex, loaded with character and charm.', '3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom upstairs.', 'A large kitchen, dining room and living room.', 'Driveway backdoor leads to the basement (and kitchen) which has a washer and dryer and plenty of space.', 'Great neighborhood.', 'Cats OK Dogs with landlord approval.', 'Recently renovated apartment.', 'Upper-level unit in a small complex with excellent off-street parking.', 'OK smoking/pets.', 'Rent includes water, sewer, trash and recycling.', '$850 per month.', 'Off street parking.', 'Large shared yard space.', 'Utilities, lawn maintenance and snow removal are the responsibility of the tenant.', 'Upper-level unit in a small complex with off-street parking.', 'The handsome stone and steel kitchen overlooks the chic living room, with a fireplace, exposed brick, hardwood floors and a built-in desk and shelves.', 'The second floor bedroom is surrounded by large windows and sliders with Juliet balconies, a newly tiled three-piece bath and convenient full-size laundry.', 'If you are interested please send me your number.', 'I will contact you soon.']
